<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Two-Factor Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #3e3e3e;
        }

        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 600px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            padding: 10px;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }

        .otp-section {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .otp {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Two-Factor Verification for <%= name %>
            </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>For added security, we require a two-factor authentication (2FA) process. Please use the OTP below to
                verify your identity. The OTP is valid for 10 minutes and can be used to complete your login or account
                action.</p>
            <div class="otp-section">
                <p>Your OTP is: <span class="otp">
                        <%= otp %>
                    </span></p>
            </div>
            <p>If you did not request this verification, please ignore this email and contact our support team if you
                notice any suspicious activity on your account.</p>
            <p>Thank you for ensuring the security of your account!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>